EEG acquisition

16 dry‑electrode EEG nodes (head) sample at 256 Hz for 10 seconds → 2560 samples per channel.

Each sample is a 24‑bit ADC value (microvolts), converted to a 32‑bit float (IEEE 754) inside the node’s microcontroller.

